OL,3,CSecretary of State challenged to take
OL,4,Cpart in 'heavy lifting' to reform
OL,5,CStormont
OL,7,FThe Northern Ireland Secretary has
OL,8,Fbeen challenged to take part in the
OL,9,F"heavy lifting" of Stormont reform, or
OL,10,Frisk sharing the blame if the
OL,11,Finstitutions collapse again.
OL,13,FAlliance Party leader Naomi Long said
OL,14,Fshe wants to approach the recently
OL,15,Freformed devolved government with
OL,16,Foptimism but warned against
OL,17,Fcomplacency.
