OL,3,CSecretary of State challenged to take
OL,4,Cpart in 'heavy lifting' to reform
OL,5,CStormont
OL,7,FAddressing her party's annual
OL,8,Fconference at the Stormont Hotel in
OL,9,Feast Belfast, Ms Long called for
OL,10,F"action to implement real and tangible
OL,11,Fprogress towards actual reform".
OL,13,FShe described her party as "the only
OL,14,Fconsistent and unequivocal champion of
OL,15,Freform of the institutions".
OL,17,FDevolution was restored in January
OL,18,Ffollowing two years of disruption
OL,19,Fafter the resignation of then First
OL,20,FMinister Paul Givan (DUP) in February
OL,21,F2022.
