OL,7,FPrior to that, the institutions
OL,8,Feffectively collapsed for three years
OL,9,Ffollowing the resignation of then-
OL,10,Fdeputy First Minister Martin
OL,11,FMcGuinness (Sinn Fein) in 2017.
OL,13,FAlliance welcomed the Irish deputy
OL,14,Fpremier and Foreign Affairs Minister
OL,15,FMicheal Martin to the conference
OL,16,Fdinner on Friday night.
