OL,5,CStormont
OL,7,FIn a speech, the Tanaiste said there
OL,8,Fis an "opportunity to begin a
OL,9,Fmeaningful conversation about reform"
OL,10,Fat Stormont, referring to "two
OL,11,Fextended periods of years of one party
OL,12,Fand then another blocking the
OL,13,Fformation of the Executive".
OL,15,F"We just cannot have another such
OL,16,Fperiod," he added.
