OL,3,CSecretary of State challenged to take
OL,4,Cpart in 'heavy lifting' to reform
OL,5,CStormont
OL,7,F"I don't think any party wants that
OL,8,Fand I am certain that the public would
OL,9,Fhave zero tolerance for another cycle
OL,10,Fof suspension, disenfranchisement and
OL,11,Fpolitical torpor."
OL,13,FAddressing the conference on Saturday,
OL,14,FMs Long said she was "encouraged by
OL,15,Fthe thoughtful and considered manner"
OL,16,Fin which she said he addressed the
OL,17,Fissue of reform, "and the need for the
OL,18,Fprocess of delivery to include all
OL,19,Fparties and both Governments".
