OL,3,CSecretary of State challenged to take
OL,4,Cpart in 'heavy lifting' to reform
OL,5,CStormont
OL,7,FMs Long said she has seen "no such
OL,8,Fcommitment" from Northern Ireland
OL,9,FSecretary Chris Heaton-Harris.
OL,11,FReferring to his hobby of
OL,12,Fweightlifting, Ms Long said: "Chris,
OL,13,FI'm calling on you to step up and do
OL,14,Fsome seriously heavy lifting on reform
OL,15,Fof the institutions, sooner rather
OL,16,Fthan later, unless you want to be
OL,17,Fpermanently burdened with a large
OL,18,Fshare of the blame of any future
OL,19,Fcollapse."
