OL,4,Cpart in 'heavy lifting' to reform
OL,5,CStormont
OL,7,FMs Long told Alliance members that
OL,8,F"ransom politics is unacceptable".
OL,10,F"I want to approach this new mandate
OL,11,Fwith optimism. To have confidence that
OL,12,Fthe last collapse was the last
OL,13,Fcollapse. To believe that we will see
OL,14,Fsustained and sustainable government,"
OL,15,Fshe said.
