OL,3,CSecretary of State challenged to take
OL,4,Cpart in 'heavy lifting' to reform
OL,5,CStormont
OL,7,F"Both are a form of ransom politics.
OL,8,FNeither is democratic or acceptable.
OL,10,F"I can see the true cost of this
OL,11,Fpolitical nihilism: in our obscene
OL,12,Fhealth waiting lists, in our failure
OL,13,Fto deliver capital investment and
OL,14,Feconomic growth, and in our creaking
OL,15,Feducation system.
OL,17,F"Our public sector workers can see it
OL,18,Fin their pay packets, as their
OL,19,Fsalaries have failed to keep pace with
OL,20,Fothers across these islands."
