OL,5,CStormont
OL,7,FMs Long said they need to see "action
OL,8,Fto implement real and tangible
OL,9,Fprogress towards actual reform".
OL,11,FShe said it is their job to make the
OL,12,Finstitutions "as stable as they can be
OL,13,Ffrom within, whilst continuing to make
OL,14,Fthe case for reform to those who have
OL,15,Fthe power to deliver it".
OL,17,F"Above all, that is the two
OL,18,Fgovernments, the joint guarantors of
OL,19,Fthe (Belfast) Agreement," she said.
